icky/Raja Babu||Bhojpuri|| [[Amrapali Dubey]], [[Antara Biswas|Monalisa]]||\n|-\n|2015 || ''Jigarwala'' ||Rahul ||Bhojpuri|| [[Amrapali Dubey]]||\n|-\n|2015 || ''[[Ghulami (2015 film)|Ghulami]]'' ||||Bhojpuri|| [[Madhu Sharma]], [[Shubhi Sharma]]||\n|-\n|2016 || ''[[Aashik Aawara]]'' || Raja/Deepak  ||Bhojpuri|| [[Aamrapali Dubey]], [[Kajal Raghwani]] ||\n|-\n|2016||''[[Bam Bam Bol Raha Hai Kashi]]''||Kashi||Bhojpuri||[[Amrapali Dubey]]||\n|-\n|2016||''Nirahua Chalal Sasural 2''||Nirahua||Bhojpuri||[[Aamrapali Dubey]]||\n|-\n|2016 || ''Aakhiri Rasta'' ||  ||Bhojpuri|| [[Rinku Ghosh]]||\n|-\n|2016 || ''Ram Lakhan'' ||Ram Yadav || Bhojpuri|| [[Aamrapali Dubey]], [[Shubhi Sharma]]||\n|-\n|2016 ||  ''Mokama 0 K.M.''  || ||Bhojpuri/Hindi || [[Aamrapali Dubey]], [[Anjana Singh]]||\n|-\n|2017 ||  ''Nirahu Satal Rahe'' ||Nirahua ||Bhojpuri/Hindi || [[Amrapali Dubey]]||<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.newsstate.com/entertainment/bhojpuri-cinema/bhojpuri-star-dinesh-lal-yadav-nirahua-aamrapali-dubey-romantic-bhojpuri-song-from-bhojpuri-movie-nirahua-satal-rahe-watch-here-95961.html|title='\u0928\u093f\u0930\u0939\u0941\u0906 \u0938\u091f\u0932 \u0930\u0939\u0947' \u0915\u0947 \u0907\u0938 \u0917\u093e\u0928\u0947 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0928\u093f\u0930\u0939\u0941\u0906 \u0914\u0930 \u0906\u092e\u094d\u0930\u092a\u093e\u0932\u0940 \u0926\u0941\u092c\u0947 \u0915\u0940 \u0926\u093f\u0916\u0940 \u091c\u092c\u0930\u0926\u0938\u094d\u0924 \u0915\u0947\u092e\u093f\u0938\u094d\u091f\u094d\u0930\u0940|last=News State Beauro|date=10 July 2019|work=News State|access-date=8 August 2019|language=Hindi}}</ref>\n|-\n|2017 || ''Jigar''||Deva || Bhojpuri||[[Anjana Singh]]||\n|-\n|2017 ||''Sipahi''|| ||Bhojpuri||[[Amrapali Dubey]]||\n|-\n|2017 ||  ''[[Nirahua Hindustani 2]]''  ||Nirahu Yadav ||Bhojpuri/Hindi || [[Amrapali Dubey]]||<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://hindi.timesnownews.com/bollywood/bollywood/article/bhojpuri-film-nirahua-hindustani-2-rocks-on-youtube-dinesh-lal-yadav-aamrapali-dubey-